UML:TaggedValue.value: Provides services on the uAAL service bus for querying devices
Sends context events for incoming sensor events to the uAAL context bus
Implement uAAL Wrappers for HW device
Refinement of HW devices to HW device model
Establishes connection to the physical HW device
Over this channel sensor messages from/to the HW device are received and sent
Two additional dependencies needed among universAAL exporter and the two buses
